text: Andreea Mitu and Elena-Gabriela Ruse were the defending champions, but chose not to participate. Xenia Knoll and Mandy Minella won the title, defeating Ylena In-Albon and Conny Perrin in the final, 6–3, 6–4. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Montreux Ladies Open - Doubles
